"```sql\nSELECT posts.Title\nFROM postLinks\nJOIN posts ON postLinks.PostId = posts.Id\nWHERE postLinks.CreationDate = (\n    SELECT MIN(CreationDate) FROM postLinks\n);\n```\n\nThis SQL query retrieves the title of the post associated with the oldest post link by finding the minimum creation date in the `postLinks` table and joining it with the `posts` table to get the corresponding title."